text: Anastasija Čemirtāne (born 17 October 1999) is a Latvian footballer who plays as a midfielder for Sieviešu Futbola Līga club Rīgas FS and the Latvia women's national team. ==References== Category:1999 births Category:Living people Category:Women's association football midfielders Category:Latvian women's footballers Category:Latvia women's international footballers Category:Rīgas FS players
